imdb.plot outline: The "World Wide Nate: African Adventures" audience vicariously experiences Africa through Nathan as he uncovers every treasure the motherland has to offer from the top of the tallest peak in Drakensberg to the deepest depths of the Indian Ocean. The "World Wide Nate: African Adventures" audience will get to see, taste, and feel all that 21st century Africa has to offer.
